trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Ink.IncrementalStrokeHitTester.StrokeHit" /> event of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.IncrementalStrokeHitTester" />.
trans-unit.target: Rappresenta il metodo che gestir√† l'evento <see cref="E:System.Windows.Ink.IncrementalStrokeHitTester.StrokeHit" /> di un oggetto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.IncrementalStrokeHitTester" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns the strokes that are a result of the eraser path erasing a stroke.
trans-unit.target: Restituisce i tratti che sono il risultato del tracciato della gomma da cancellare che cancella un tratto.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> that contains the strokes that are created after the eraser path erases part of <see cref="P:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke" />.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection" /> che contiene i tratti creati dopo che il tracciato della gomma da cancellare cancella parte dell'oggetto <see cref="P:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.GetPointEraseResults%2A> method returns a <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection> that contains the strokes that result in the eraser path erasing the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke%2A> where they intersect.
trans-unit.target: Il <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.GetPointEraseResults%2A> metodo restituisce un <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection> che contiene i tratti che comportano la cancellazione di percorso gomma il <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke%2A> in cui si intersecano.

trans-unit.source: If the eraser path intersects the middle of <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke%2A>, the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.GetPointEraseResults%2A> method returns a <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection> that contains two new strokes.
trans-unit.target: Se il percorso di gomma interseca il centro di <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.HitStroke%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeHitEventArgs.GetPointEraseResults%2A> metodo restituisce un <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection> che contiene due tratti nuovi.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke" /> that is intersected by the eraser path.
trans-unit.target: Ottiene l'oggetto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke" /> che viene intersecato dal tracciato della gomma da cancellare.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke" /> that is intersected by the eraser path.
trans-unit.target: Oggetto <see cref="T:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke" /> che viene intersecato dal tracciato della gomma da cancellare.
